3 = = = = = = CLOSED = = = = = =  This place has folded, & it's not a big surprise.  Starting out as an excellent Hometown Buffet, it changed to 5-Star Zen Buffet.  Then, & also after a name change only to Jen Buffet, it continued to be a top favorite of my Yelp friends & I.  Then it was sold & became City Buffet here.  They ruined the beautiful look of the place, took out many of the food selections, tried to upsell you to renting a little stove to cook part of your own lunch, & other kookie things.  It's no surprise that the place didn't last long.  Now the building has been leased by the Min Lu family & will reopen this Spring as a Yummy Grill Buffet like their one in Chandler.  I can't wait!!     :-))
